{"tid":1782441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你是忘記了還是害怕想起來","createTime":"2019-12-14T03:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T10:57:23.000Z","uid":340074,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5319c567506ad4e052ccc4ebc9d6b4e23cd94811","tid":1782441,"uid":340074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"前幾日睇咗返校<br />\n當中有句名台詞<br />\n「你是忘記了還是害怕想起來？」<br />\n睇到呢一句<br />\n我開始驚<br />\n我係驚<br />\n香港人會忘記<br />\n或者係害怕想起這恐佈的歲月<br />\n我明直到現在<br />\n發生咗好多事<br />\n死傷無數<br />\n但即時係咁<br />\n我地都要時刻回想<br />\n呢件事所帶俾我地既教訓<br />\n埸仗仲未打完<br />\n我地要努力地活下去<br />\n<br />\n最後附上返校作曲人給香港人的說話<br />\n<br />\n「活下去，才有希望。在未來才會有人知道，這一切多麽得來不易；我希望在不久的將來，這一切可以陽光普照。致自由。」"},{"pid":"82afe80bda8253a58ce641940b3519191d821494","tid":1782441,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T03:06:41.000Z","msg":"唔好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cadbc225caa5f3759b6179b08fedb513228c96e","tid":1782441,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T10:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}